'''{{class|Actor}}'''

{{c|void '''CopyBloodColor''' (Actor ''other'')}}

==Usage==
Changes the {{Property|BloodColor|blood color}} of the calling actor to match that of the specified actor.

===Parameters===
*{{c|Actor '''other'''}}
:A pointer to the actor from which to get the blood color.

